data.description: ***Multiple Offers Received*** Please submit final offers.This beautiful home offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience, just moments away from schools, parks, shopping centers, and recreational facilities. A well-manicured lawn and tasteful landscaping create an inviting first impression. Step inside to discover a meticulously maintained interior and an open-concept design that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and a spacious island. This home offers generously sized bedrooms and a primary bedroom with en-suite bathroom. A covered patio offers a shady retreat for outdoor dining and relaxation, while the fenced yard ensures privacy and security. A two-car garage provides ample storage and parking space. Little Elm is known for its friendly atmosphere and community spirit. Residents enjoy access to parks, lakes, and various recreational activities and are within the Little Elm ISD.
